▶【Proweful Suction】: This stick vacuum cleaner is equipped with a 600W strong motor, can generate up to 17000Pa powerful suction, perfect for hardwood floors, marble floors, tile, low pile carpet and can easily pick up all kinds of particles like dust, pet hair, pet litter, food scraps, etc.

▶【Easy To Use】: This vacuum cleaner pet hair is easy to operate. One-click can start the vacuum, no need to keep pressing the switch. ▶【Lightweight】: The main motor is 3.9 pounds and the ergonomic handle allows use with just one hand. More convenient use for the elderly, children, and pregnant women. ▶【Large Capacity】: Extra large 0.8 L dustbin with one press button for easy empty and can captures dirt and pet hair without leakage.
